<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA4">
<l>eṉṉiṉ mikupukaḻār yāvarē piṉṉaiyumaṟ</l>
<l>ṟeṇṇiṉ mikupukaḻēṉ yāṉallā leṉṉa</l>
<l>karuñcōtik kaṇṇaṉ kaṭalpuraiyuñ cīlap</l>
<l>peruñcōtik keṉṉeñcāṭ peṟṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who will have more praise than me afterwards, again</l>
<l>when one considers, apart from me who has much praise,</l>
<l>having obtained my heart [to be] the servant of the great light</l>
<l>with an ocean-like nature, my Kaṇṇaṉ of black light?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
